                <p>Neither the author nor the type of this <term key="Qene">qǝne</term> are indicated 
                    in the manuscript. 
                    It has been printed in <bibl><ptr target="bm:Afawarq1984Yageezqeneyat"/>
                        <citedRange unit="page">66-67</citedRange></bibl>, together 
                    with an Amharic translation, the type being defined as 
                    <term key="Mibazhu">mi-bazḫu</term> (composed of three lines). 
                    The manusript witness <ref type="mss" corresp="BNFabb145"/>
                    shows a slight text variation (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ተሣህሎ፡</foreign> instead of 
                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተሰቅሎ፡</foreign> as in the printed edition).</p>
